abstract: >
  FinNutriAgent is an agentic AI framework that jointly optimizes household
  meal planning and financial budgets under nutritional, cultural, and
  economic constraints. It combines Mixed-Integer Linear Programming,
  multi-agent reasoning, and LLM orchestration to produce cost-effective,
  nutritionally complete, halal-compliant weekly meal plans evaluated on
  a synthetic dataset reflecting realistic Saudi Arabian household conditions.
keywords:
  - agentic AI
  - meal planning
  - nutritional optimization
  - household budgeting
  - linear programming
  - halal diet
  - Saudi Arabia
  - food security
  - multi-agent systems
